OL,5,Cfinish
OL,7,FRace organisers in are investigating
OL,8,Fthe result of this year's Beijing
OL,9,Fafter accusations that a trio of
OL,10,Frunners deliberately threw the race.
OL,12,FHe Jie - who is considered one of
OL,13,FChina's most promising long-distance
OL,14,Frunners - emerged victorious one
OL,15,Fsecond ahead of three African runners,
OL,16,Fincluding Kenyan athlete Robert Keter
OL,17,F- who is the former 5km world record-
OL,18,Fholder.
