OL,5,Cfinish
OL,7,FVideo footage of the finish to
OL,8,FSunday's race shows fellow Kenyan
OL,9,Fathlete Willy Mnangat turn toward He
OL,10,Fand gesture him to move ahead of
OL,11,Fhimself, Keter and Ethiopia's Dejene
OL,12,FHailu.
OL,14,FAll three runners then appear to hold
OL,15,Fback behind He and watch on as he
OL,16,Ffinished in first place.
OL,18,FHe, despite winning, appears to look
OL,19,Ffar less enthused than the three
OL,20,FAfrican runners, who can be seen
OL,21,Fapplauding the 25-year-old's success.
