OL,7,FHe later told reporters he "was not in
OL,8,Fmy best competitive state", but did
OL,9,Fnot discuss the controversial finish.
OL,11,FThe result prompted some Chinese
OL,12,Finternet users to call for an
OL,13,Finvestigation, with one writing on
OL,14,Fsocial platform Weibo that "fair play
OL,15,Fis vital".
OL,17,FAnother wrote: "The so-called 'ways of
OL,18,Fthe world' should not taint the
OL,19,Ffairness of competition in sports.
OL,20,FFairness is always at the core of
OL,21,Fsporting spirit."
