OL,7,FRace organisers the Beijing Municipal
OL,8,FSports Bureau and Chinese Athletics
OL,9,FAssociation acknowledged "feedback has
OL,10,Fbeen received" and "will be processed
OL,11,Ffurther", Chinese state media reported.
OL,13,FChinese sports company Xstep, which
OL,14,Fsponsors both He and the Beijing Half
OL,15,FMarathon, told Chinese state-run
OL,16,Foutlet The Paper that the situation is
OL,17,F"being investigated and verified by
OL,18,Fmultiple parties".
